1585
01:08:47,058 --> 01:08:49,045
Gong Yoo, the pork belly is so delicious.

1586
01:08:49,045 --> 01:08:52,006
It's good, right? It's delicious.

1587
01:08:52,006 --> 01:08:54,417
[Yum!]

1588
01:08:58,847 --> 01:09:01,128
It tastes like garlic bossam. I love it.

1589
01:09:01,128 --> 01:09:03,660
[The perfect example of crispy outside
and juicy inside, bursting with flavor]

1590
01:09:03,660 --> 01:09:06,120
[A special meal made with care and effort]
- It's so delicious. - Right.

1591
01:09:06,120 --> 01:09:08,746
Everything is so delicious.

1592
01:09:09,612 --> 01:09:11,397
[For the 10th anniversary party,
