1596
01:09:19,401 --> 01:09:22,889
Yeah, that would be the best.

1597
01:09:22,889 --> 01:09:24,150
Wow, but having a barbecue party

1598
01:09:24,150 --> 01:09:25,990
- while looking at the ocean is really...
- Exactly.

1599
01:09:25,990 --> 01:09:27,607
Right.

1600
01:09:27,607 --> 01:09:29,710
- This is so nice right now.
- Seriously.

1601
01:09:29,710 --> 01:09:30,958
