1604
01:09:37,357 --> 01:09:39,291
- I think it's been over a year...
- Oh, really?

1605
01:09:39,291 --> 01:09:41,177
especially the East Sea.

1606
01:09:41,177 --> 01:09:42,772
What about you, El?

1607
01:09:42,772 --> 01:09:45,506
I actually really like coming to this area.

1608
01:09:45,506 --> 01:09:46,974
