1613
01:09:58,523 --> 01:10:01,054
- Oh, you rinse off with it?
- Yeah.

1614
01:10:01,054 --> 01:10:03,023
Then I go to a nearby buckwheat noodle place,

1615
01:10:03,023 --> 01:10:04,635
- eat some noodles, and go home.
- Oh, my.

1616
01:10:04,635 --> 01:10:07,208
- Why, why?
- Ah, Yoo In Na, seriously...

1617
01:10:07,208 --> 01:10:10,134
[Terrible reenactment]
- What? - "You rinse off with it?"

1618
01:10:10,134 --> 01:10:13,121
When did she ever do that? When?

1619
01:10:13,121 --> 01:10:15,407
When did she do that?

1620
01:10:16,000 --> 01:10:17,939
So you're a P, a P.

1621
01:10:17,939 --> 01:10:19,559
Oh, she's a P.

1622
01:10:19,559 --> 01:10:20,680
[Extroverted ENFP (spontaneous type)]
- E. - I...

1623
01:10:20,680 --> 01:10:22,339
