1624
01:10:22,339 --> 01:10:23,579
Oh...

1625
01:10:23,579 --> 01:10:26,045
So you were just pretending
to be shy with your expression?

1626
01:10:26,045 --> 01:10:30,792
[An ESFJ who quickly closes the distance]

1627
01:10:30,792 --> 01:10:31,950
Right?

1628
01:10:31,950 --> 01:10:33,625
