- They're the same age. - Same age.

1629
01:10:33,625 --> 01:10:34,635
Oh, really?

1630
01:10:34,635 --> 01:10:37,545
- They're the same age, but it's a bit awkward.
- Awkward same-age friends.

1631
01:10:37,545 --> 01:10:38,873
I'm not awkward.

1632
01:10:38,873 --> 01:10:41,169
Didn't you two sit together
