1634
01:10:44,825 --> 01:10:47,519
[Photo taken at the Guardian wrap party]
[In Na, Lee El, Go Eun]

1635
01:10:47,519 --> 01:10:50,190
Look, you were sitting right
next to each other.

1636
01:10:50,190 --> 01:10:52,992
Wow, you were really young.

1637
01:10:52,992 --> 01:10:55,519
- Really? Does that mean we got old?
- What?

1638
01:10:55,519 --> 01:10:58,032
- No, you look the same. I was surprised.
- I look the same, right?

1639
01:10:58,032 --> 01:11:01,979
- I thought it was taken just recently.
- Jeez.

1640
01:11:02,588 --> 01:11:05,740
You know those over-the-top
