1641
01:11:05,740 --> 01:11:08,531
You're really good at those, aren't you?

1642
01:11:08,531 --> 01:11:09,852
No, I'm telling the truth.

1643
01:11:09,852 --> 01:11:11,392
[Approved]

1644
01:11:11,392 --> 01:11:13,058
I can't believe you.

1645
01:11:13,058 --> 01:11:14,544
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

1646
01:11:14,544 --> 01:11:16,413
- Oh, my.
- Oh, my.

1647
01:11:16,413 --> 01:11:18,163
[The smooth talker who wins hearts]

1648
01:11:18,163 --> 01:11:21,973
Then what scary scene from Guardian
do you remember the most?

1649
01:11:21,973 --> 01:11:24,474
For me, there was a scene

1650
01:11:24,474 --> 01:11:30,016
where Eun Tak's mom is holding
baby Eun Tak and looking at her in bed.

1651
01:11:30,016 --> 01:11:33,742
There were spirits around her
staring in black and white...

1652
01:11:33,742 --> 01:11:35,356
- Right, right.
- from outside the window.

1653
01:11:35,356 --> 01:11:37,795
- It really scared me.
- Outside the window, right.

1654
01:11:37,795 --> 01:11:39,588
