1655
01:11:40,708 --> 01:11:45,714
[The Goblin's bride who was born
against the fate of death]

1656
01:11:51,383 --> 01:11:53,730
<i>- It's the Goblin's bride.
- Yeah, the Goblin's bride.</i>

1657
01:11:53,730 --> 01:11:56,369
<i>- The Goblin's bride...
- The Goblin's bride has been born.</i>

1658
01:11:56,369 --> 01:12:02,240
[Countless spirits watching the Goblin's bride]

1659
01:12:03,709 --> 01:12:06,383
That part was scary for me.

1660
01:12:07,141 --> 01:12:08,915
That part was a bit scary.

1661
01:12:08,915 --> 01:12:13,021
When Eun Tak was talking
with the killer from up high...

1662
01:12:13,021 --> 01:12:16,588
- Because his wife died unfairly...
- Yeah, yeah.

1663
01:12:16,588 --> 01:12:18,714
Your wife that you killed!

1664
01:12:18,714 --> 01:12:21,584
