1665
01:12:21,584 --> 01:12:23,130
[Eyes turning cold]

1666
01:12:23,130 --> 01:12:25,368
Oh...

1667
01:12:25,368 --> 01:12:27,914
You want to die too, don't you?

1668
01:12:29,308 --> 01:12:32,924
[The danger of death that came to Eun Tak]

1669
01:12:32,924 --> 01:12:35,130
Oh...

1670
01:12:35,130 --> 01:12:37,510
death by falling.

1671
01:12:37,510 --> 01:12:40,503
I wasn't going to use
my boyfriend advantage, but...

1672
01:12:42,456 --> 01:12:45,477
