1677
01:13:11,173 --> 01:13:12,860
This has never happened to me before.

1678
01:13:12,860 --> 01:13:14,393
[Good connections left behind by a great work]
- It's my first time too. - Right.

1679
01:13:14,393 --> 01:13:16,320
- It's probably everyone's first time.
- Yeah.

1680
01:13:16,320 --> 01:13:18,853
It's really my first time
having people remember it like this

1681
01:13:18,853 --> 01:13:22,339
